reviewText: I have tried to watch this $25.00 DVD several times, and it puts me to sleep every time.  I thought it was just me, and had my husband try (to learn somthing) and he zonked out too.  SO, if you need a great nap and don't mind spending that much money...go for it.  As far as the vendor, it got here in no time at all, the sale and delivery was great.
